battleball (2.0-15) unstable; urgency=low

  * Updated debian menu for menu systems that don't evaluate $DISPLAY; now
    uses "sh -c" and exec (closes: #245697).
  * Moved menu pixmap to /usr/share/pixmaps.
  * Updated build-depends to reflect new X11 package splits.

 -- Chris Waters <xtifr@debian.org>  Fri, 21 May 2004 12:58:21 -0700

